{"tid":2352381,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 鵪鶉強燒賣 蟲草花綿花雞 必食叉燒酥 蒜蓉鮮蝦春卷","createTime":"2021-01-04T04:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T12:04:32.000Z","uid":33359,"like":93,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"2047797e791302867532b3f2b7ea7be66b55e7dc","tid":2352381,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9fNMMAH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9fNMMAH.jpg&h=627378a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sGmAt5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sGmAt5.jpg&h=aaf8274e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NcebXHs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNcebXHs.jpg&h=39ba6508&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ajo8fua.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fajo8fua.jpg&h=c2236d57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6k9n4nx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6k9n4nx.jpg&h=eebe9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鵪鶉強燒賣有啲普通<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話特別好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蟲草花綿花雞好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個啲我分唔到係豬皮定係魚肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為個樣似豬皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但食落係魚肚既口感<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要索哂啲湯汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好入味好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞肉都好嫩滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叉燒酥有啲可惜係拎到返黎已經唔熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但仲係食到好酥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我相信熱食應該會好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鮮蝦春卷唔洗多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n招牌點心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又香又脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落條腰椎L1L2節好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be84073ac84923df66c642cb12a5d3f7a4f78f8","tid":2352381,"uid":8304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:03:32.000Z","msg":"where<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3386196f5f9eb85131d44af569ed8925b1de8e","tid":2352381,"uid":317749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7464b3474e2654e1e3e5f80918f30c9d07b610c6","tid":2352381,"uid":367007,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:03:51.000Z","msg":"點心師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860cbb400fb2b0bdbb2551d41f0ddaf8d3f3498c","tid":2352381,"uid":33359,"like":8,"dislike":37,"score":-29,"quote":{"pid":"5be84073ac84923df66c642cb12a5d3f7a4f78f8","tid":2352381,"uid":8304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:03:32.000Z","msg":"where<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:03:54.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0972def52fa316c47cd6c2645034ccd64cf4c3c9","tid":2352381,"uid":291750,"